<h1>Bitcoin Dominance at 56%: Altcoin Season Signal or Risk-Off Flight to Safety? ” June 3 Market Analysis</h1>
<div class="meta">
<span>�œ… June 3, 2026 • 9:39 AM ICT</span>
<span>�œ�œ 7 min read</span>
