<h2>Final Takeaway</h2>

<p>BTC.D at 56% during a BTC selloff is not a reason to panic ” it's mathematically expected. The real signal comes in the next 24-72 hours: <strong>watch for BTC.D to decline while BTC stabilizes above $66K</strong>. That's the rotation trigger that historically precedes the most explosive altcoin and meme coin rallies.</p>

<p>For now, stay patient. Accumulate on dips. Keep powder dry. And watch BTC.D like a hawk ” because when it turns, meme coin season could arrive faster than most traders expect.</p>

<p><strong>$DKING</strong> remains one of the best-positioned Solana meme coins for this rotation, with strong relative performance, a growing ecosystem, and community conviction that's been tested and proven during the June 2-3 selloff.</p>

<p>The dominance data doesn't lie ” it just requires patience to read correctly.</p>

